snippet.title: Monster Hunter Rise: Sunbreak - Release Date Announcement - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Monster Hunter Rise: Sunbreak comes to Nintendo Switch 6/30/22! Journey to the west as you face a powerful new trio known as the ‘Three Lords’.

With a new story, new monsters, and a Master Rank quest difficulty, your adventure continues this June!

https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/monster-hunter-rise-sunbreak-switch/
https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/monster-hunter-rise-sunbreak-deluxe-edition-switch/
